---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import henrique from '../images/henrique.jpg';
---

<section class='wrapper'>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='info'>
      <h2 class='lf-semibold'>Who We Are</h2>
      <p class='sans-regular'>
        Henrique, with a decade of experience in financial consulting, leads the
        business with a deep understanding of strategic planning and market
        analysis. His expertise spans budgeting, forecasting, financial
        planning, and funding acquisition.
      </p>
      <p class='sans-regular'>
        Adept at optimising business operations through process improvements,
        task automation, and resource management. He also champions the use of
        technology to enhance efficiency and fosters a culture of innovation,
        helping businesses stay competitive by developing and improving products
        and services. His comprehensive approach ensures clients are
        well-equipped to navigate industry trends and achieve their goals.
      </p>
    </div>
    <Image
      class='image'
      src={henrique}
      alt='Henrique'
      width='318'
      height='359'
    />
  </div>
</section>

<style lang='scss'>
  @import '../styles/variables.scss';

  section {
    background-color: $dark;
    color: $white;
  }

  h2 {
    border-bottom: 0.125rem solid $white;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 7fr 3fr;
    align-items: center;
    grid-gap: 1.5rem;

    > :first-child p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .image {
      border-radius: 1rem;
      justify-self: flex-end;
      align-self: flex-end;
    }
  }
</style>
